        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Armed Prohibited Persons Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of Justice to make grants to states to develop and operate systems to retrieve firearms from armed prohibited persons. An armed prohibited person is a person who lawfully purchases a firearm and later becomes prohibited from possessing the firearm due to an act or omission committed by such person.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
